FINAL EVENT - SAVE THE DATE

We are excited to invite you to the RESCUER Final Conference and 2nd RESCUER Post Pilot Workshop, where we will unveil the future of first responder tools and technologies. The event is scheduled for 11-12th of June, 2024, at Hospital de Emergencias Enfermera Isabel Zendal, Madrid. Join us as we showcase the H2020 RESCUER project, highlighting the project's results and future development potential from both technical and end-user perspectives. 

What to expect?  

  • Discover the advances of RESCUER project with insightful presentations. 

  • Learn from technology, research, and first responder organizations that have co-developed the RESCUER tools and technologies, sharing their experience gained through 2 rounds of pilots in 3 different use case scenarios.  

  • Exchange ideas on future needs and options in first responders’ tools, technologies and beyond. 

  • Participate in interactive workshops and join panel discussion covering topics related to future ideas from the technical perspective, as well as the perspective of end-users. 

  • Connect with project partners and participants from across Europe.  

To secure your spot at this knowledge-packed two-day event, please register by clicking in here or button on the right.

We are looking forward to your attendance at this groundbreaking event, which will influence the effectiveness of first responders. 

Do not hesitate to contact us for any further information or clarification.
